Package: pkginspectr
Title: Tidy Tools for Inspecting and Comparing R Package Structure
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Daniel", "Dauber", , "daniel.dauber.io@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Daniel Dauber [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Daniel Dauber <daniel.dauber.io@gmail.com>
Description: Inspect the structure and source code of R packages with a tidy, minimal interface. Provides tools to summarise file counts, folder structure, and lines of code across R packages, whether local or hosted on GitHub. Designed for speed, extensibility, and compatibility with tidy workflows. Visualise results using built-in ggplot2 support, and compare multiple packages side by side to spot patterns or explore code scale.
